1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,820
Boss, is there any new stock?

3
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:13,940
It's here.

4
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:14,920
I've saved some for you.

5
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,300
Let me know when the new stock arrives.

6
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:20,380
Of course.

7
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:21,520
We're old friends, after all.

8
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:22,420
I'm heading out.

9
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:34,500
Hey buddy, want some discs?

10
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,660
Western, Japanese, Korean,

11
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:36,820
I have them all.

12
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:38,610
I've got a business here

13
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,530
that's much more
profitable than selling discs.

14
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:41,660
Are you interested?

15
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,240
What's that?

16
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,380
Selling this.

17
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:51,790
(Peidun Cough Syrup)
It keeps the miners alert.

18
00:02:52,090 --> 00:02:53,660
It makes way more than selling discs.

19
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,710
Can you really make money with this?

20
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:01,020
You'll know once you try it.

21
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:08,020
=Episode 3=
(The Honey Trap)

22
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:10,620
Everyone, get inside.

23
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:11,780
Police inspection!

24
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,470
Turn on the lights, turn off the music.

25
00:03:14,070 --> 00:03:14,980
Everyone, stop.

26
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:16,220
Over here.

27
00:03:16,220 --> 00:03:17,860
Men in one line, women in the other.

28
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,700
Stand straight.

29
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:19,740
Li, come here.

30
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:20,700
Take him.

31
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,560
Get him sorted.

32
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,420
Line up.

33
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:23,550
Quickly!

34
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,970
Men in one line, women in the other.

35
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,510
Spot check.

36
00:03:26,510 --> 00:03:27,350
Take a paper cup.

37
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:28,200
We're doing urine tests in a moment.

38
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,040
Step aside.

39
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,160
Can you just give me two bottles?

40
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,020
Just two bottles.

41
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:32,140
I really can't take it anymore.

42
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:33,080
You're addicted.

43
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,450
I just couldn't resist
having one bottle.

44
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,320
Men in one line, women in the other.

45
00:03:38,430 --> 00:03:39,310
Move it.

46
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:40,660
- Get over here.
- It's all the same.

47
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:42,250
- Police spot check.
- Line up.

48
00:03:42,250 --> 00:03:44,100
- Line up.
- Form two lines.

49
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:44,940
Go to the restroom.

50
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:46,590
Men in one line, women in the other.

51
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:47,620
Take a paper cup.

52
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,840
We're doing urine tests in a moment.

53
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,740
Hurry up.

54
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:50,650
Dad,

55
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:51,810
- what's going on?
- Move it.

56
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:52,930
It's a spot check.

57
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:54,720
Why didn't you give us a heads-up?

58
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:55,700
A heads-up?

59
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,270
That would defeat the whole purpose, no?

60
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,780
Stop arguing.

61
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:01,580
I can't handle this all by myself.

62
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:03,740
I'll go help out.

63
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:04,580
Go ahead.

64
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:05,720
Master, I'm going over.

65
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:06,560
Alright.

66
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,060
Come on, line up here. Over this way.

67
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:08,980
He hasn't paid yet.

68
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:09,820
I've got it.

69
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:10,990
Here's your money.

70
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,100
Next.

71
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:43,980
(Men's Restroom)

72
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:49,490
Whose were those size 36 shoes just now?

73
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,420
Mine.

74
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,500
Head upstairs. Come on.

75
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:03,020
- Why did she faint?
- Songge.

76
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:04,100
Someone fainted!

77
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:04,980
What happened to her?

78
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,370
She fainted.

79
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:08,060
Songge.

80
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:09,580
Songge.

81
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:10,980
Songge.

82
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:11,990
What's wrong?

83
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:16,580
Songge,

84
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,560
what's wrong with you?

85
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:20,220
Mr. Chen, I think my blood sugar is a bit low.

86
00:05:20,540 --> 00:05:21,420
From exhaustion?

87
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,540
Lin,

88
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,380
come here.

89
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:24,310
Take her to rest.

90
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:26,660
She can do the test after resting.

91
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,500
Easy now.

92
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,520
Take it slow.

93
00:05:30,540 --> 00:05:31,380
Dad,

94
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:33,580
why don't I go first?

95
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:35,560
That way, I can look after Songge.

96
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,180
Fine.

97
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:39,180
Limin.

98
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,020
Test Hui first.

99
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,420
- Alright.
- Go on then.

100
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:45,060
- Come on.
- Move forward.

101
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:46,580
You, come out first.

102
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:56,660
(Men's Restroom)

103
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:11,480
Officer Lin, I have low blood sugar,

104
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,620
and I haven't had dinner yet.

105
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,600
Could you help me heat up my food?

106
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:15,780
Sure.

107
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:16,650
Just lie back down.

108
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:17,780
Thank you.

109
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,140
Hui.

110
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:42,940
Hui.

111
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,250
Hui!

112
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,340
Hui!

113
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:56,540
You brat, what are you doing?

114
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,620
I couldn't pee earlier,

115
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:58,500
but now I have.

116
00:06:58,580 --> 00:06:59,620
Fine, hurry up.

117
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:03,740
Come on, next.

118
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:07,860
Chen Hui.

119
00:07:09,050 --> 00:07:09,890
Chen Hui.

120
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:15,700
All set.

121
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:37,860
Over there.

122
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:44,950
What's wrong with you?

123
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:48,330
Urine test. Move it.

124
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:53,920
Hurry up, now.

125
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:06,230
How are you feeling?

126
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:08,790
Much better.

127
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,260
Songge, go get in line first.

128
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:22,180
Go.

129
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:31,260
Name?

130
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:32,940
Wang Dali.

131
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,300
Do you have ID?

132
00:08:34,300 --> 00:08:35,140
Let me see it.

133
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:36,420
I was just passing by

134
00:08:36,420 --> 00:08:37,540
when you guys brought me in.

135
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:38,790
I don't have it.

136
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:41,060
Do you remember your ID number?

137
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,580
It's so long,

138
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:43,740
who could remember that?

139
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:44,820
I never need it anyway.

140
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:46,500
Wang Dali.

141
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,340
No. 33.

142
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:48,500
Noted.

143
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:51,780
Go wait over there.

144
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:52,780
There are only a few left.

145
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:53,900
I'll notify you all
once the testing is done.

146
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,100
When your name is called,

147
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,690
you're coming back
to the station with us.

148
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:07,610
Zhang Mingyuan.

149
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:11,640
Li Xiaojun.

150
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,010
Zhang Hai.

151
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:17,510
Zhao Qiang.

152
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:31,820
Li Zhijun.

153
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,140
Present.

154
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,340
Hurry up.

155
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:35,180
Take him away.

156
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:41,500
Listen up.

157
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:42,820
This

158
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,810
spot check

159
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,140
is over.

160
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:48,700
Thank you

161
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:49,620
for your cooperation.

162
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:51,220
The roller skating rink

163
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:52,100
can resume business.

164
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:54,740
Strange.

165
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:56,400
Where did my lens case go?

166
00:10:12,620 --> 00:10:13,900
Why did he faint?

167
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,220
- Songge, are you okay?
- Someone fainted!

168
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,740
- This woman passed out.
- Songge.

169
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,140
Songge.

170
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:22,540
(Water Tank)

171
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,980
Page me,

172
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,430
23768.

173
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:35,540
Leave a message,

174
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:36,380
water tank.

175
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:38,500
(Water Tank)

176
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:09,940
Come here, miss.

177
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,320
Come over for a moment.

178
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:12,860
Your friend's name is Wang Sui?

179
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:14,460
Yes.

180
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:15,660
It's just as you said.

181
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:17,940
She is indeed a college student,

182
00:11:17,970 --> 00:11:19,500
and she has no prior criminal record.

183
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:20,820
Tell her,

184
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,260
once the fine is paid tomorrow,

185
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,140
she can go home.

186
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,220
How much is the fine?

187
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,060
Three thousand.

188
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:27,540
Three thousand...

189
00:11:27,540 --> 00:11:28,660
Have a good talk with her.

190
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:30,060
Tell her to focus on her studies

191
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:31,970
and stay away from places like that.

192
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:32,980
Understand?

193
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:34,100
Yes, thank you.

194
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:46,380
What are you looking for?

195
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:48,230
My contact lens case is missing.

196
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:49,540
It's a tiny little case

197
00:11:49,540 --> 00:11:50,850
with my contacts inside.

198
00:11:50,850 --> 00:11:51,740
Have you seen it?

199
00:11:51,740 --> 00:11:53,100
Contact lenses?

200
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,050
I think I just saw it.

201
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:56,070
Let me check for you.

202
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:57,420
Thanks.

203
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:04,740
Is it this one?

204
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:06,220
Yeah.

205
00:12:06,220 --> 00:12:07,120
Where did you find it?

206
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,740
I just finished cleaning the restroom.

207
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:12,900
I reckon someone probably threw it
in there by mistake.

208
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:15,260
How could it be there?

209
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:22,100
(Vienna Cabaret)

210
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:36,810
Yu.

211
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:37,660
Mr. Yang.

212
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:38,660
Are you looking for me?

213
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:40,460
Mr. Yang, here's the thing.

214
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,120
I've run into some trouble lately,

215
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:43,340
and I wanted to ask

216
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:44,180
to borrow some money.

217
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,540
I thought it was something serious.

218
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:47,580
How much?

219
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:48,740
Three thousand yuan will do.

220
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:52,700
Well,

221
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:53,980
how about after work,

222
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:55,700
we go book a room

223
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:56,540
and have a good chat?

224
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,780
Why book a room?

225
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:02,260
We're both adults.

226
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,620
What else would we do in a room?

227
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:09,320
Forget it. I'm not borrowing.

228
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,810
- Get lost!
- Hey, wait.

229
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:11,670
Get lost!

230
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,710
Yu, if you don't want to, fine.

231
00:13:12,710 --> 00:13:13,800
I'll still lend it to you.

232
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:16,100
Yu.

233
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:17,380
Get lost, you creep!

234
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,260
What are you looking at?

235
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,730
Hurry up.

236
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:01,740
- Take it over there.
- Move faster.

237
00:14:01,740 --> 00:14:04,220
(Victim, murder weapon, glass shards)

238
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,260
Director Tong.

239
00:14:06,260 --> 00:14:07,140
Chief Liu.

240
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:09,460
Well?

241
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:10,540
Did you find anything

242
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:11,980
in this night raid?

243
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:15,300
This night raid covered

244
00:14:15,300 --> 00:14:16,540
eight entertainment venues

245
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:18,180
in Fengyang.

246
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:20,340
We found six people
positive for ketamine

247
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:22,140
and twelve positive for Kejianin.

248
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,420
It's just a pity

249
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:24,900
that they were all buyers.

250
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:26,420
We didn't catch a single seller.

251
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:28,080
This group is organized

252
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,380
extremely tightly.

253
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,620
This is quite strange.

254
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:32,020
The whole thing is strange.

255
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:33,540
The trail goes cold here again.

256
00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:35,510
I always feel like these people

257
00:14:35,570 --> 00:14:36,870
are always one step ahead of us.

258
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:37,940
Don't be discouraged.

259
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:40,180
It's because our work
isn't thorough enough.

260
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:41,020
Understood?

261
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:45,380
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

262
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:03,300
Today was really dangerous.

263
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,400
Lu Yuan is the only one right now

264
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:06,340
who has seen our faces.

265
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,220
With him roaming outside,

266
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:11,230
he's a ticking time bomb for us.

267
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:15,340
I've been thinking.

268
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:18,420
Actually, he can't produce

269
00:15:18,420 --> 00:15:19,910
any evidence against us.

270
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,180
Even if he calls the police

271
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:23,310
or gets caught,

272
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,490
the police won't just believe
everything he says, right?

273
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:28,140
Besides, didn't you tell me once

274
00:15:28,140 --> 00:15:29,500
that a single witness isn't proof?

275
00:15:31,620 --> 00:15:32,660
That's true.

276
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:34,900
But if he identifies us,

277
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,900
the police will get involved.

278
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,460
No matter how well we hide,

279
00:15:39,460 --> 00:15:41,300
the police will keep
an eye on us for a while.

280
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:43,910
Then we won't be able
to move any stock for a long time.

281
00:15:44,190 --> 00:15:45,620
Your illness can't wait any longer.

282
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,500
So, what do you want to do?

283
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:56,140
Take a gamble.

284
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:58,140
Have Lu Yuan come over tomorrow.

285
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:11,570
Director Chen,

286
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:12,500
you have a call.

287
00:16:12,940 --> 00:16:13,780
Okay.

288
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:17,900
Hello?

289
00:16:19,260 --> 00:16:20,100
What?

290
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:30,460
Chief Liu.

291
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,460
Chief, stop knocking.

292
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:32,420
I've been knocking for 20 minutes.

293
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:33,260
It's no use.

294
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:35,180
Maybe she went out?

295
00:16:35,180 --> 00:16:36,860
No, she goes downstairs
to eat every day.

296
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:38,260
I haven't seen her go down today.

297
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:39,940
Chief Liu.

298
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:42,060
Chief Liu!

299
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:43,790
Look, I have the key.

300
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:45,030
Why don't you go in and check?

301
00:16:45,220 --> 00:16:47,060
You have a keycard?
Why didn't you say so sooner?

302
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:49,600
Well, she's a police officer,
and a lady on top of that.

303
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,820
- How would I dare...
- Hurry up and open it.

304
00:16:50,820 --> 00:16:51,760
Alright, I'm opening it.

305
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:55,100
Are you kidding me?

306
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:55,940
Chief Liu.

307
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,020
Don't you know how
to knock before entering?

308
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:10,660
Chief Liu.

309
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:11,940
Are

310
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:12,820
you okay?

311
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,620
I'm fine.

312
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:16,180
What's the big hurry?

313
00:17:18,340 --> 00:17:19,180
Right.

314
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:20,220
It's my fault.

315
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:21,060
Carry on then.

316
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:25,810
Chief Liu,

317
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:26,660
so

318
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:28,340
you found something new?

319
00:17:29,090 --> 00:17:30,260
I don't think this is working.

320
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,010
Ever since we discovered

321
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:33,750
someone was selling
Peidun Cough Syrup in Fengyang,

322
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:34,920
Lu Yuan took off immediately.

323
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:36,850
They're spooked now.

324
00:17:36,850 --> 00:17:38,010
They've been in hiding for a while.

325
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,790
So, what do you think

326
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:42,780
we should do?

327
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,260
Back to the old approach.

328
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:47,460
Find a way to identify the victim,
and then screen their social circle.

329
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:49,450
The body was burnt to nothing.

330
00:17:49,450 --> 00:17:50,450
How do we investigate?

331
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:52,940
Tang sent me
an autopsy report last night.

332
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:54,500
It mentioned
the victim's right heel bone

333
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:55,620
was more worn down than the left.

334
00:17:55,620 --> 00:17:57,100
(Bone wear on the right heel)

335
00:17:57,100 --> 00:17:58,620
The high-heeled shoe heel

336
00:17:59,060 --> 00:18:01,030
found at the scene back then

337
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:02,660
(Sole)
also proved this.

338
00:18:02,660 --> 00:18:05,020
This lump of material
is the plastic sole from the shoe.

339
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:06,620
This is a heel.

340
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,220
That's the issue.

341
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:16,100
Why did she

342
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:17,660
only attach a sole to one shoe?

343
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:19,140
It can only mean

344
00:18:19,380 --> 00:18:20,500
she consistently put

345
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,940
more weight on
her right foot than her left.

346
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:25,080
That's why the right heel

347
00:18:25,180 --> 00:18:26,620
was worn down so badly.

348
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:27,980
A limp.

349
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:29,890
Someone with a limp
wouldn't wear high heels.

350
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:31,050
Normal daily life

351
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:32,220
wouldn't cause wear like this.

352
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:34,260
It must have been caused
by her work environment.

353
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,220
Director Chen,

354
00:18:36,390 --> 00:18:37,660
with your knowledge of Fengyang,

355
00:18:37,820 --> 00:18:38,860
any ideas where to look?

356
00:18:40,940 --> 00:18:42,460
(Right-foot high heel from the scene)

357
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,350
In Fengyang,

358
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:46,100
there actually is such a place.

359
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:49,100
The people working there

360
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:52,220
only wear out their right heels.

361
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:10,020
(Huabo Art Products Processing Factory)

362
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:10,900
A processing factory?

363
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:15,020
Three years ago, this man

364
00:19:15,730 --> 00:19:16,860
opened a factory here.

365
00:19:17,500 --> 00:19:18,420
He said

366
00:19:18,580 --> 00:19:19,700
he was using jet

367
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,540
to make jewelry.

368
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:21,820
Making jewelry?

369
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,740
Jet.

370
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:25,620
In the past,
when it was dug out of the mine,

371
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:27,630
it was all treated as waste
and thrown away.

372
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:29,210
I didn't understand it then.

373
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,940
I thought these guys

374
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:33,380
were just using it as a cover
to do something illegal.

375
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:34,540
So I watched them for a while.

376
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:35,750
I eventually noticed

377
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,330
the workers there

378
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,290
had very heavy wear

379
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:40,810
on their right heels.

380
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:44,240
If it weren't for this case,
I would've forgotten all about it.

381
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:46,220
Let's go.

382
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:50,460
Who is it?

383
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,060
Police.

384
00:19:55,340 --> 00:19:56,270
Chi Huabo, right?

385
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:58,540
We're from the police station.

386
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,380
I know.

387
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:00,540
You're Director Chen.

388
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,310
You don't remember me?

389
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,910
My dad was in the ventilation zone
of Mine No. 3.

390
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,660
Right.

391
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,430
Back then,

392
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:11,220
you got into
the city's normal college, didn't you?

393
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:13,740
That was over ten years ago.

394
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:15,460
Director Chen,

395
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,780
is there something you need?

396
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:18,980
We'd like to

397
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:20,140
ask you a few questions.

398
00:20:20,140 --> 00:20:20,980
Can we come in?

399
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:23,700
Sure.

400
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:39,900
This business pays pretty well,
doesn't it?

401
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,340
Not bad.

402
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:44,380
Better than digging coal in the mines.

403
00:20:48,210 --> 00:20:49,460
This is carborundum, right?

404
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:50,460
Yes.

405
00:20:50,460 --> 00:20:52,380
We use it to polish the jet.

406
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:13,220
Why are there no workers here today?

407
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:14,740
They're on break.

408
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:16,110
I'm planning to close up for a while.

409
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:18,380
Why?

410
00:21:19,390 --> 00:21:20,820
I need to go do some market research,

411
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,100
see if there are

412
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:23,420
any new styles out there.

413
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,180
When are you leaving?

414
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:26,200
Tonight's train.

415
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,900
I'm heading to the city
with some samples.

416
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,660
How many workers
do you usually have here?

417
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:35,350
(Piecework: Tan Wen, Anita Mui, Jiang Xue)
Seven or eight, I'd say.

418
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,660
Men or women?

419
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,020
All women.

420
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:40,220
This kind of work is too tedious for men.

421
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:46,820
Director Chen.

422
00:21:49,060 --> 00:21:49,900
What is this?

423
00:21:52,020 --> 00:21:53,380
Some people like the vintage style.

424
00:21:53,380 --> 00:21:54,220
They like the texture.

425
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,580
We use this to distress the items.

426
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:56,960
Why is the water this color?

427
00:21:57,300 --> 00:21:58,220
What's in here?

428
00:21:58,220 --> 00:21:59,620
It contains lime,

429
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,630
caustic soda,

430
00:22:00,630 --> 00:22:01,820
and potassium permanganate.

431
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:03,580
Sir and madam,

432
00:22:03,580 --> 00:22:04,580
is there anything else?

433
00:22:05,180 --> 00:22:06,460
I'm in a hurry to catch a train.

434
00:22:06,520 --> 00:22:07,980
I won't make it if I don't leave now.

435
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:09,280
Chi Huabo,

436
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:11,260
I'm afraid that today,

437
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:13,060
you really can't leave.

438
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:16,680
(Confess for leniency,
resist for severity)

439
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:19,470
Did you register the IDs
of these female workers you hired?

440
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:20,620
No.

441
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,380
You hire people
without even checking IDs?

442
00:22:23,380 --> 00:22:25,020
This work is dirty and exhausting.

443
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:26,500
No locals are willing to do it.

444
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:29,420
They're mostly the families of those
at the illegal coal pits.

445
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,860
Director Chen, you know those people.

446
00:22:30,860 --> 00:22:32,500
Many of them don't have IDs.

447
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:36,540
You should at least know their names.

448
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:39,020
There are names
on the piecework sheet in my office.

449
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:40,700
But whether they're real or fake,

450
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:41,860
it's hard to say.

451
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,060
Do you have their contact info?

452
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:43,900
No.

453
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,160
Then, when you
come back from out of town,

454
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,300
how do you tell them to start work?

455
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:47,580
I pay by the piece,

456
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:48,600
settled daily.

457
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:49,660
When it's time to work,

458
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:51,020
I just hang

459
00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:52,300
a hiring sign on the front gate.

460
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:53,460
Those who want to work

461
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:54,540
will show up on their own.

462
00:22:57,940 --> 00:22:58,780
Alright.

463
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:03,190
It seems you don't know anything at all.

464
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,300
It's not that,

465
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:06,780
I really don't know, Director Chen.

466
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,090
Not knowing stuff

467
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:09,700
is not against the law, right?

468
00:23:25,540 --> 00:23:26,380
You're here.

469
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,380
Come.

470
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:37,060
Hui,

471
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:38,260
playing ball?

472
00:23:45,820 --> 00:23:46,660
Where's the stuff?

473
00:23:56,020 --> 00:23:57,370
You're a man of great wealth, Boss.

474
00:23:57,740 --> 00:23:59,720
This is just
a drop in the bucket for you...

475
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:05,700
You want it?

476
00:24:08,140 --> 00:24:09,450
Let's get things straight first.

477
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:13,860
Go ahead.

478
00:24:14,980 --> 00:24:16,100
You broke the rules.

479
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:18,300
The rules were set

480
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,140
before the deal.

481
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:21,860
We won't be supplying you anymore.

482
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:24,020
Don't do that.
You're cutting off my lifeline, Hui.

483
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:25,860
You brought it on yourself.

484
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:29,980
Just give me one bottle first, okay?

485
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:37,340
I'm begging you.

486
00:24:37,340 --> 00:24:38,380
Just give me one bottle.

487
00:24:38,380 --> 00:24:39,700
I haven't touched that stuff in so long.

488
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:40,980
I want it... I...

489
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:42,740
Just one bottle, Hui.

490
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:45,260
I'll do anything you want, please.

491
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:46,580
Your words.

492
00:24:49,020 --> 00:24:50,220
The heat is on out there now.

493
00:24:50,860 --> 00:24:52,180
The goods can't be moved for sure.

494
00:24:53,020 --> 00:24:53,940
But you have a choice.

495
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:55,980
What choice?

496
00:24:57,140 --> 00:24:58,060
Leave Fengyang.

497
00:25:01,220 --> 00:25:03,420
There are 50,000
and ten bottles of drugs in this bag.

498
00:25:03,420 --> 00:25:04,420
We'll give it all to you.

499
00:25:05,380 --> 00:25:06,580
But you must guarantee

500
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:07,620
that from now on,

501
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:09,350
you'll act like you never met us.

502
00:25:15,940 --> 00:25:16,780
Fine.

503
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:17,770
Fine.

504
00:25:17,770 --> 00:25:18,620
I...

505
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:20,210
I'll leave.

506
00:25:20,210 --> 00:25:21,220
I'll never come back.

507
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:22,820
How can we trust you?

508
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,260
Hui,

509
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:34,660
I, Lu Yuan, am a man of my word.

510
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:35,820
I won't come back.

511
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:37,230
If I do, I'm a dog.

512
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:49,810
Listen,

513
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:51,300
this is the only time

514
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:52,300
and the last time.

515
00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:54,530
If you dare come back,

516
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:56,180
I will never let you off.

517
00:26:28,220 --> 00:26:29,060
Boss.

518
00:26:31,300 --> 00:26:32,580
I'm never coming back.

519
00:26:32,580 --> 00:26:33,420
Don't worry.

520
00:27:09,740 --> 00:27:11,780
Regarding yesterday's drug test,
someone faked it.

521
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:19,660
Master.

522
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:20,500
Chief Liu.

523
00:27:20,900 --> 00:27:22,900
Chi Huabo's drug test results are out.

524
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:26,100
It's negative.

525
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:28,220
And at that coal gangue dump,

526
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,140
they didn't find

527
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,240
any Peidun Cough Syrup.

528
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:31,640
Did you check

529
00:27:32,020 --> 00:27:32,860
the piecework sheets?

530
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:35,700
Yes. No one was at the station
applying for a residence permit.

531
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:37,180
How many of them are there?

532
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:39,060
There are only
piecework sheets from last month.

533
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:40,190
Thirteen people in total.

534
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,340
The longest stayed for a month,

535
00:27:41,340 --> 00:27:42,910
while the shortest stayed
for only a day or two.

536
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:44,380
Fengyang isn't that big.

537
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:45,310
If we can find two or three,

538
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:46,740
we should be able
to find out about the others.

539
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:47,680
That's going to be hard.

540
00:27:48,500 --> 00:27:49,340
Take a look.

541
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:51,700
This list even has Anita Mui

542
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:52,780
and Yang Yuying on it.

543
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:55,140
Why would these people
use aliases just for a manual job?

544
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:56,580
The people coming to work
from the illegal coal pits

545
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:58,140
all have very complicated backgrounds.

546
00:27:58,220 --> 00:27:59,900
Some are running from marriages,
some are dodging debts,

547
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:02,180
and some have
criminal records or priors.

548
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:03,660
Every year, we catch

549
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,820
quite a few of them here.

550
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:06,470
Potassium permanganate,

551
00:28:06,850 --> 00:28:08,100
carborundum abrasives,

552
00:28:08,390 --> 00:28:09,480
and wear on the right heel.

553
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:11,250
All three conditions match.

554
00:28:11,740 --> 00:28:13,150
Chi Huabo still wants to leave town.

555
00:28:13,150 --> 00:28:14,060
He must have a problem.

556
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:15,690
But the problem now is

557
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:17,420
we have too little information.

558
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:18,860
It's hard to get him to talk.

559
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:23,180
In Fengyang,

560
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:24,980
I don't believe

561
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:26,660
he can hide anything from me.

562
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:30,060
Yesterday, when I put
my contact lens case on the front desk,

563
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:31,140
you were right there.

564
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:32,340
You must have taken it.

565
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:35,380
Are you okay?

566
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:36,900
There were so many people there.

567
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:38,420
You're saying
I was the only one near you?

568
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,460
Don't you just want my dad's help?

569
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:41,890
That's no way to ask for a favor.

570
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,210
I've already solved the problem.

571
00:28:45,210 --> 00:28:46,270
I don't need your help.

572
00:28:46,280 --> 00:28:48,000
And you don't need
to put on an act for me.

573
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:50,000
I see people like you all the time.

574
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:52,700
If you want me to pretend
I don't know anything, that's fine.

575
00:28:53,660 --> 00:28:54,530
Lend me 3,000 yuan.

576
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:55,780
I'll pay you back in two months.

577
00:28:56,940 --> 00:28:58,060
Are we even that close?

578
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:59,220
Why should I lend you money?

579
00:28:59,230 --> 00:29:00,920
So you don't want
to settle this quietly?

580
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:02,470
Then I'll go
to the police station right now

581
00:29:02,470 --> 00:29:03,460
and tell them everything.

582
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:06,260
Go ahead.

583
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,940
Let the police come and check again.

584
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:09,010
I gave you a chance.

585
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:10,500
Just you wait.

586
00:29:12,860 --> 00:29:13,700
Xin Yu.

587
00:29:17,340 --> 00:29:18,760
You're Han Ning's friend, right?

588
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,020
Why are you borrowing money?

589
00:29:20,020 --> 00:29:21,820
Did something happen?

590
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:23,350
My friend tested positive.

591
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,500
The police caught her.

592
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:26,220
She needs to pay
the fine to be released.

593
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,560
I've asked everyone,
but I can't find the money.

594
00:29:28,570 --> 00:29:29,460
I see.

595
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:31,900
Xin Yu,

596
00:29:32,210 --> 00:29:33,700
we really didn't know

597
00:29:33,810 --> 00:29:35,060
about what you just said.

598
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:37,850
But if you go to the station
and they come to investigate,

599
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:39,330
tell me,

600
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:41,140
how are we supposed to do business?

601
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,830
Customers have been sparse lately.

602
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:45,900
We're all neighbors here.

603
00:29:45,910 --> 00:29:47,380
We should look out
for each other, right?

604
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:48,250
Yes.

605
00:29:48,250 --> 00:29:49,380
I'm not that kind of person.

606
00:29:50,060 --> 00:29:51,380
I just have no other choice.

607
00:29:52,300 --> 00:29:53,140
Alright.

608
00:29:53,700 --> 00:29:54,860
As long as we're clear.

609
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,100
We can lend you this money.

610
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:58,500
But

611
00:29:58,820 --> 00:29:59,860
I have one condition.

612
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:02,900
What condition?

613
00:30:03,980 --> 00:30:06,420
Three thousand yuan
isn't a small amount.

614
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,370
We'll give you the money,

615
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:10,500
but you have to sing here
for free for two weeks.

616
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:13,380
This money will count
as your performance fee.

617
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:20,330
Business lately
hasn't been as good as before.

618
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:23,110
These past couple of days,
Chen Hui and I have been discussing

619
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:23,970
what we should do.

620
00:30:23,970 --> 00:30:25,010
If you come sing for us,

621
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:27,130
on one hand,
it'll solve your financial problems,

622
00:30:27,340 --> 00:30:28,420
and on the other hand,

623
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:30,320
it'll help us attract more customers.

624
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:31,320
It's a win-win.

625
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:32,160
What do you think?

626
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:34,900
I need to get the money today.

627
00:30:35,980 --> 00:30:36,900
No problem.

628
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,740
Right, Chen Hui?

629
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:40,300
It's up to you.

630
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,180
Then, let me get ready.

631
00:30:43,190 --> 00:30:44,500
I'll give you the money tonight.

632
00:30:46,780 --> 00:30:48,520
This contact lens case
is already worn out.

633
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:49,740
Later, Chen Hui and I

634
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:50,900
will buy a new one for you.

635
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:53,140
No, that's okay.

636
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:54,200
I can buy one myself.

637
00:30:55,220 --> 00:30:56,060
I'm sorry.

638
00:30:56,430 --> 00:30:58,020
I was just in a rush.

639
00:30:58,120 --> 00:30:59,380
I didn't come here to cause trouble.

640
00:30:59,380 --> 00:31:00,220
It's fine.

641
00:31:00,220 --> 00:31:01,060
I understand.

642
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,380
If it were my friend,

643
00:31:02,380 --> 00:31:04,320
I'd also be trying
everywhere to borrow money.

644
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:06,060
Okay.

645
00:31:06,060 --> 00:31:06,900
See you tonight.

646
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:08,300
See you tonight.

647
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:22,980
(Fengyang Coal Mine Guesthouse)

648
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:26,100
Let me ask you something.

649
00:31:27,980 --> 00:31:29,060
Do you know Chi Huabo?

650
00:31:30,300 --> 00:31:31,300
Yes, I do.

651
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:33,140
The guy who does those jet carvings.

652
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:34,260
Has he come here

653
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,470
with any women?

654
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:40,740
Be honest.

655
00:31:41,890 --> 00:31:43,380
Well, we have a woman here...

656
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,260
Just speak.

657
00:31:45,300 --> 00:31:46,140
He has.

658
00:31:46,580 --> 00:31:48,090
But he hasn't successfully landed many.

659
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:49,500
You know better than he does?

660
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,380
If he had landed them,

661
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:53,170
he'd have taken them
upstairs for a room.

662
00:31:53,690 --> 00:31:55,300
Lately, when he comes here,

663
00:31:56,020 --> 00:31:57,460
what kind of woman has he brought?

664
00:31:58,060 --> 00:32:00,060
The recent one was the most clingy.

665
00:32:02,090 --> 00:32:02,970
Southern accent.

666
00:32:03,340 --> 00:32:04,180
Slender.

667
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:05,300
Fair-skinned.

668
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:06,460
Are there

669
00:32:06,460 --> 00:32:07,540
any more distinct features?

670
00:32:08,060 --> 00:32:09,380
I didn't really notice that.

671
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:11,900
What's wrong?

672
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:13,180
Is it hard to say?

673
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:14,530
No, let me think.

674
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:16,740
Right.

675
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:18,860
She liked wearing high heels.

676
00:32:18,860 --> 00:32:20,640
But with those heels, you know,

677
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:22,220
only one of them was soled.

678
00:32:24,460 --> 00:32:25,310
Are you sure?

679
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:26,690
Only one of her shoes was soled?

680
00:32:27,060 --> 00:32:27,930
Positive.

681
00:32:27,930 --> 00:32:29,900
When she walked down the hall at night,

682
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:32,020
you could hear the rhythm.

683
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:38,060
What is her name?

684
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:41,180
I heard him call her Susu.

685
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:42,540
Susu?

686
00:32:44,860 --> 00:32:45,820
I have a photo.

687
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,220
You took these secretly, didn't you?

688
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:02,240
How is it a secret?

689
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:03,830
Why did you take

690
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:04,740
so many of these?

691
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:09,060
These people all get rooms by the hour.

692
00:33:09,060 --> 00:33:10,580
In case something happens,

693
00:33:10,580 --> 00:33:11,420
maybe I can

694
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:12,900
be of help to you guys.

695
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:13,740
Yang Baichun,

696
00:33:14,140 --> 00:33:15,300
I've found that you are

697
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:16,340
not just annoying,

698
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:18,330
but also very disgusting.

699
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:19,900
Find it.

700
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:23,500
Whether it's disgusting or not,
just say if it helped you or not.

701
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:24,380
This is the one.

702
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:30,340
Director Chen,

703
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,220
(Liusan Mutton Restaurant)
how did you know Chi Huabo

704
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,640
would take women to the guesthouse?

705
00:33:34,490 --> 00:33:35,740
In Fengyang,

706
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:37,600
it's only an 800-meter radius area.

707
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:39,020
Look at Chi Huabo,

708
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:40,140
he smokes a pipe

709
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:41,060
and wears a tie.

710
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:42,540
Why?

711
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:44,500
Because he likes it.

712
00:33:44,500 --> 00:33:45,740
Like it, my foot!

713
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,580
He likes...

714
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:48,100
I'm sorry.

715
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:49,860
My language is a bit crude.

716
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:53,110
It's not that he likes it,
so what was the reason?

717
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:54,740
He's just

718
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:57,140
pretending

719
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,300
to be important.

720
00:33:59,030 --> 00:34:00,110
I'm telling you, Chief Liu,

721
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,000
when a boss

722
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:01,920
and a female employee

723
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,700
have something shady going on,

724
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:05,910
then it's definitely

725
00:34:05,910 --> 00:34:06,900
some kind of affair.

726
00:34:07,980 --> 00:34:09,140
For guys like that,

727
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,650
besides the wining and dining,

728
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:12,060
they have to go shopping

729
00:34:13,260 --> 00:34:14,500
and book a room.

730
00:34:14,640 --> 00:34:16,340
But in a place like Fengyang,

731
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:17,690
most businesses

732
00:34:17,690 --> 00:34:20,140
basically cater to the miners.

733
00:34:20,780 --> 00:34:22,460
This place doesn't appeal to them.

734
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,740
So there is really only one place

735
00:34:25,540 --> 00:34:27,180
they would like to visit.

736
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:29,060
The guesthouse?

737
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,710
Exactly. This guesthouse

738
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:32,180
is where the leaders host guests.

739
00:34:32,330 --> 00:34:34,890
In terms of the general vibe,

740
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:37,060
it's a high-class place.

741
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:38,740
Chi Huabo has been

742
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:40,340
a child of the mine since he was little.

743
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:42,430
Never mind how much
of the world he's seen,

744
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:44,140
his petty mindset

745
00:34:44,140 --> 00:34:46,060
will never change,
and it can't be hidden.

746
00:34:47,170 --> 00:34:48,060
I'm full.

747
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,480
Let's go back
and continue the interrogation.

748
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:50,740
Chief Liu,

749
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:54,420
I suggest waiting until tomorrow
to question Chi Huabo again.

750
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,090
Why?

751
00:34:56,740 --> 00:34:59,660
Look at him. Since he got here,
he's been acting all tough and arrogant.

752
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:00,500
Just ignore him.

753
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:02,710
Lock him up for the night.

754
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:05,000
The more you ignore him,
the more nervous he'll get.

755
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:06,500
By tomorrow,

756
00:35:06,810 --> 00:35:07,800
he'll have

757
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:10,620
scared himself to death.

758
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,260
Recognize her?

759
00:35:18,220 --> 00:35:19,460
She was blackmailing me.

760
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:20,660
From the beginning.

761
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:22,180
What's this woman's name?

762
00:35:22,180 --> 00:35:23,100
How do you know her?

763
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:24,020
Her name is Yu Susu.

764
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:26,100
She's a worker at my factory.

765
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:27,420
And then?

766
00:35:28,900 --> 00:35:30,380
And then we slept together.

767
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:31,850
She was willing.

768
00:35:31,850 --> 00:35:33,240
I never forced her.

769
00:35:33,660 --> 00:35:34,710
How did she blackmail you?

770
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:36,570
She said she'd sue me for rape.

771
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:37,780
She said she had evidence

772
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:39,140
and wanted 200,000 yuan.

773
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:40,520
I don't have that kind of money.

774
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:41,620
When did this happen?

775
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,020
October 2.

776
00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:44,970
The specific time?

777
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:47,260
It was almost noon that day.

778
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:48,980
She came to see me.

779
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:50,780
Bo,

780
00:35:51,610 --> 00:35:52,820
I'm leaving Fengyang next week.

781
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:53,820
I won't be coming back.

782
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:55,300
Not coming back?

783
00:35:57,340 --> 00:35:58,240
Then what about us?

784
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:00,140
Didn't I say it that day?

785
00:36:00,140 --> 00:36:01,170
The elders at home are sick,

786
00:36:01,170 --> 00:36:02,600
so I have to go back
and look after them.

787
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:04,860
But, you know,

788
00:36:04,860 --> 00:36:07,180
I've been a bit short on cash lately.

789
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:11,380
If you're doing well,
could you lend me a few thousand first?

790
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:12,700
With our relationship,

791
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:13,860
why even talk about "lending"?

792
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:15,700
This is all the cash I have on me now.

793
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:16,740
Take it all.

794
00:36:16,740 --> 00:36:17,940
What kind of person do you take me for?

795
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:19,540
I've been with you for half a year.

796
00:36:19,660 --> 00:36:21,300
How many meals did you take me out for?

797
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,360
You only bought me two pairs of shoes.

798
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:24,060
Even if I were a girl
at a massage parlor,

799
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:25,100
it wouldn't be that cheap.

800
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:26,150
Susu,

801
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,740
what are you saying?

802
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:29,090
Don't we have love between us?

803
00:36:29,090 --> 00:36:29,940
What love?

804
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:30,820
One price.

805
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:31,740
Twenty thousand yuan.

806
00:36:32,140 --> 00:36:33,230
Give me the money,

807
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,970
and I won't make things
hard for you anymore.

808
00:36:34,980 --> 00:36:35,820
Otherwise,

809
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:36,860
believe it or not,

810
00:36:36,860 --> 00:36:39,780
I'll go to the police station right now
and say you raped me.

811
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:42,240
Did you have any contact after that?

812
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,190
No contact.

813
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,420
Is it that there is no contact,

814
00:36:44,430 --> 00:36:45,920
or that there's
no need to contact anymore?

815
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:47,580
What do you mean?

816
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:48,580
She threatened you.

817
00:36:49,380 --> 00:36:50,220
So,

818
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:52,620
you killed her.

819
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:54,820
What?

820
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:56,740
Yu Susu is dead?

821
00:36:56,740 --> 00:36:57,580
Sit down.

822
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:58,700
It wasn't me.

823
00:36:59,260 --> 00:37:00,100
I didn't kill anyone.

824
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:00,940
Listen!

825
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:02,100
Yu Susu is dead.

826
00:37:03,070 --> 00:37:05,100
Regarding the Beimianling murder case,
right now,

827
00:37:05,220 --> 00:37:06,860
you are the prime suspect.

828
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:08,000
It really wasn't me.

829
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,020
I didn't kill anyone.

830
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:10,500
How can you prove you didn't do it?

831
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,510
I really didn't kill anyone.

832
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:15,470
Have you seen this before?

833
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:18,180
Never.

834
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:19,700
Then,

835
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:21,740
you must have seen this.

836
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:24,100
I haven't seen that either.

837
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:25,570
No?

838
00:37:26,700 --> 00:37:28,280
Then why did you want to leave Fengyang?

839
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:31,260
I couldn't explain my way out of this.

840
00:37:31,270 --> 00:37:33,160
Besides, her husband
digs coal at an illegal coal pit.

841
00:37:33,160 --> 00:37:34,280
I was afraid he'd come beat me up.

842
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,420
Why were you so certain

843
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:36,940
that Yu Susu's husband
would come after you?

844
00:37:36,940 --> 00:37:39,220
They are a bunch of desperate thugs
who'd do anything for money.

845
00:37:39,220 --> 00:37:41,280
She definitely would have
come back to me for money.

846
00:37:41,290 --> 00:37:42,900
The more I thought about it these
last few days, the more scared I got.

847
00:37:42,900 --> 00:37:46,180
I had no other choice, so I thought
I'd go away to hide for a bit.

848
00:37:47,500 --> 00:37:50,620
Where does Yu Susu's husband dig coal?

849
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:52,050
In Liugou.

850
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:54,530
The pit entrance is halfway up the hill
at the west end of the village.

851
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:55,910
I'd dropped her off there a few times.

852
00:37:57,940 --> 00:37:58,980
Three 3s, three 4s.

853
00:37:58,980 --> 00:37:59,820
Do you have them?

854
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:00,660
No, right?

855
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:04,600
What are you playing? I'm higher.

856
00:38:11,350 --> 00:38:12,300
Don't move!

857
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,660
- Police!
- Don't move!

858
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:15,100
- Grab him!
- Get him down from there!

859
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:16,430
- Don't move!
- Get down!

860
00:38:16,430 --> 00:38:17,290
Come here!

861
00:38:17,290 --> 00:38:19,220
- Get down!
- Get down!

862
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,540
Who is the mine owner?

863
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:32,540
Speak up!

864
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,340
Are you the mine owner?

865
00:38:40,460 --> 00:38:41,300
Are you?

866
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:44,680
Then why aren't you saying anything?

867
00:38:45,900 --> 00:38:46,740
What's going on?

868
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:48,900
This man has gone crazy.

869
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:51,060
He knocked down
all the support pillars in the shaft.

870
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:53,280
We are conducting
safety production education.

871
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:55,220
I think you're the one
who needs education.

872
00:38:56,580 --> 00:38:57,450
Let me ask you,

873
00:38:57,450 --> 00:38:58,690
do you have someone here

874
00:38:58,820 --> 00:38:59,660
named Zhu Qiang?

875
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:02,260
That's him.

876
00:39:04,100 --> 00:39:05,180
Is he Zhu Qiang?

877
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:10,340
Look at me.

878
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:11,460
Is your name Zhu Qiang?

879
00:39:12,870 --> 00:39:13,900
Are you Zhu Qiang?

880
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:19,310
Do you recognize this woman?

881
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:21,600
Zhu Qiang's wife,

882
00:39:21,740 --> 00:39:22,580
Yu Susu.

883
00:39:23,420 --> 00:39:24,260
Susu!

884
00:39:24,420 --> 00:39:25,420
- Hold him down!
- Susu!

885
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:26,380
Susu!

886
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,380
What's his deal?

887
00:39:27,380 --> 00:39:29,290
I don't know.
He's been acting crazy lately.

888
00:39:29,290 --> 00:39:30,270
Like he's possessed.

889
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,830
He ruined his brain by drinking a drug.

890
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:36,900
Drinking what drug?

891
00:39:39,220 --> 00:39:40,240
His wife got it for him,

892
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:41,340
something called

893
00:39:41,580 --> 00:39:42,420
cough syrup.

894
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:44,620
Cough syrup?

895
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:46,930
Where is Zhu Qiang's dorm?

896
00:39:47,940 --> 00:39:48,780
Over there.

897
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:54,180
Which bed is Zhu Qiang's?

898
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:55,420
That one.

899
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,420
Chief Liu,

900
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:06,500
look.

901
00:40:10,780 --> 00:40:11,980
So many bottles.

902
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:13,820
Did Zhu Qiang drink all these himself?

903
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:15,820
I don't know.

904
00:40:16,620 --> 00:40:17,860
Anyway, this bag is his.

905
00:40:18,660 --> 00:40:19,500
Take it.

906
00:40:19,500 --> 00:40:20,340
Get out.

907
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:26,420
Director Chen, this pair of shoes
also has the right heel soled.

908
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:28,200
The victim is Yu Susu.

909
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:29,370
(Sole)
There's no doubt about it now.

910
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:30,740
Chief Liu,

911
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,140
next,

912
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:33,330
interrogate Zhu Qiang.

913
00:40:33,330 --> 00:40:34,180
Okay.

914
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:35,940
(Fengyang Mine Workers' Hospital)

915
00:40:36,470 --> 00:40:37,500
Have you seen this before?

916
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:39,580
No.

917
00:40:40,850 --> 00:40:42,350
When was the last time

918
00:40:42,420 --> 00:40:43,260
you saw Yu Susu?

919
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,180
I think...

920
00:40:46,220 --> 00:40:47,250
October 2.

921
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,540
She went out early this morning.

922
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:50,420
Have you contacted her since?

923
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:52,340
No.

924
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:54,480
I was working at the coal pit.

925
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:56,230
It's been so many days.

926
00:40:57,260 --> 00:40:58,380
Why didn't you report it?

927
00:40:58,410 --> 00:41:00,060
Susu can't bathe at the coal pit,

928
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,420
so every few days,

929
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,180
she goes to a hotel in town.

930
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:06,980
Sometimes she stays
for a day or two before coming back.

931
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:07,980
This time,

932
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:09,580
it has been a bit long.

933
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:11,700
I was thinking about calling the police,

934
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:13,430
but the mine owner wouldn't let me.

935
00:41:13,820 --> 00:41:15,050
He's afraid the police

936
00:41:15,050 --> 00:41:16,330
will find the illegal coal pit

937
00:41:16,690 --> 00:41:17,580
and shut it down.

938
00:41:18,350 --> 00:41:20,510
Do you know where Yu Susu's
household registration is?

939
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,790
I only know she's from around Yunchuan.

940
00:41:23,180 --> 00:41:24,420
I don't know the specifics.

941
00:41:24,820 --> 00:41:26,110
Do you have her family's number?

942
00:41:26,780 --> 00:41:27,620
No.

943
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:29,200
She's your wife,

944
00:41:30,500 --> 00:41:31,500
and you never asked her?

945
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:34,210
Susu said she ran away from a marriage.

946
00:41:34,450 --> 00:41:35,700
Her family sold her

947
00:41:35,700 --> 00:41:37,550
to a bachelor in his fifties.

948
00:41:37,940 --> 00:41:39,740
She didn't dare
let them know where she was,

949
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,540
so she didn't contact them.

950
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:45,780
Where did these bottles
of cough syrup under your bed

951
00:41:45,780 --> 00:41:46,620
come from?

952
00:41:46,620 --> 00:41:48,000
Susu brought them back.

953
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:49,940
She said she

954
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,860
bought them at Fengyang Pharmacy.

955
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:57,030
Does Yu Susu have
any relatives or friends here?

956
00:41:57,750 --> 00:41:59,520
Susu doesn't seem to

957
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:00,980
know many people around here.

958
00:42:02,310 --> 00:42:04,420
Other than her colleagues
at the factory,

959
00:42:06,220 --> 00:42:08,340
there's the owner of the lottery shop,

960
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,220
Cai.

961
00:42:09,220 --> 00:42:11,700
Susu and I met there
while buying lottery tickets.

962
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:14,860
Chief Liu,

963
00:42:15,260 --> 00:42:16,970
I think Yu Susu

964
00:42:16,970 --> 00:42:17,820
is a bit suspicious.

965
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,180
Tell me your thoughts.

966
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:21,010
Look at

967
00:42:21,010 --> 00:42:22,240
those people we caught

968
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:23,710
drinking cough syrup
in Fengyang last time.

969
00:42:23,930 --> 00:42:25,500
We've only seen it sold loose,

970
00:42:25,790 --> 00:42:26,900
put into tube popsicles.

971
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:27,940
I just don't understand

972
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:28,840
where Yu Susu

973
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:31,030
managed to get

974
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:31,870
the whole bottles.

975
00:42:32,660 --> 00:42:34,620
So, does it mean Yu Susu

976
00:42:34,620 --> 00:42:35,620
is a seller,

977
00:42:35,940 --> 00:42:36,840
just like Lu Yuan?

978
00:42:37,180 --> 00:42:38,450
She doesn't seem like a seller.

979
00:42:38,850 --> 00:42:40,210
We didn't find any bottling tools.

980
00:42:41,030 --> 00:42:43,510
She must have gotten the cough syrup
directly from the source.

981
00:42:43,820 --> 00:42:45,140
That seems unlikely, right?

982
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:46,420
Why unlikely?

983
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:48,940
Although we haven't

984
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:50,220
caught the dealer yet,

985
00:42:50,430 --> 00:42:52,550
from the information we have

986
00:42:52,550 --> 00:42:54,060
on these lower-level sellers,

987
00:42:54,220 --> 00:42:56,030
they all share a common trait.

988
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:57,500
They're male,

989
00:42:58,230 --> 00:42:59,280
over forty,

990
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:00,820
unmarried,

991
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:02,260
and have no bad habits.

992
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:04,140
The impression they give

993
00:43:04,570 --> 00:43:06,080
is that they're honest, simple,

994
00:43:06,170 --> 00:43:07,190
and hardworking.

995
00:43:08,220 --> 00:43:09,240
I see what you mean.

996
00:43:09,750 --> 00:43:10,660
This drug trafficker

997
00:43:10,660 --> 00:43:13,460
is very selective
when choosing downline sellers.

998
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:17,100
Since this group of sellers

999
00:43:17,740 --> 00:43:18,690
is very low-profile,

1000
00:43:19,380 --> 00:43:20,940
it's been very hard for us

1001
00:43:20,940 --> 00:43:21,780
to discover this.

1002
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:25,780
But this Yu Susu

1003
00:43:25,780 --> 00:43:26,790
is not the same

1004
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:28,150
as those people.

1005
00:43:28,290 --> 00:43:29,810
Don't you find it very strange?

1006
00:43:34,620 --> 00:43:35,800
(China Welfare Lottery)
Good luck to you.

1007
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:36,820
Thanks, boss.

1008
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:37,740
Here.

1009
00:43:39,140 --> 00:43:39,980
Your change.

1010
00:43:48,620 --> 00:43:49,500
You're Cai, right?

1011
00:43:49,500 --> 00:43:50,710
We're from the police station.

1012
00:43:51,300 --> 00:43:53,420
We'd like to ask you some questions.

1013
00:43:53,700 --> 00:43:54,610
Director Chen,

1014
00:43:55,140 --> 00:43:56,260
I recognize you.

1015
00:43:56,400 --> 00:43:58,340
What would you like to know?

1016
00:43:59,270 --> 00:44:00,320
You know Yu Susu?

1017
00:44:00,620 --> 00:44:01,460
I do.

1018
00:44:01,820 --> 00:44:02,660
You're quite close?

1019
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:04,100
Not really.

1020
00:44:05,040 --> 00:44:06,400
We're both from Yunchuan.

1021
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:08,820
She likes to play Happy Poker.

1022
00:44:08,820 --> 00:44:09,740
When she comes by,

1023
00:44:09,740 --> 00:44:11,030
we just chat for a bit.

1024
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:12,210
What is "Happy Poker"?

1025
00:44:12,500 --> 00:44:13,340
This is it.

1026
00:44:14,010 --> 00:44:15,370
(Happy Poker, Face Value 2 Yuan)
Scratch it to win a prize.

1027
00:44:17,190 --> 00:44:18,340
When was the last time

1028
00:44:18,340 --> 00:44:19,220
you saw Yu Susu?

1029
00:44:19,780 --> 00:44:21,150
I think

1030
00:44:21,620 --> 00:44:23,140
it was last month.

1031
00:44:25,180 --> 00:44:26,290
I was wondering

1032
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:28,240
why she hasn't come by lately.

1033
00:44:30,430 --> 00:44:31,420
What happened to her?

1034
00:44:31,430 --> 00:44:33,330
Does Yu Susu have
any other acquaintances in Fengyang?

1035
00:44:33,340 --> 00:44:34,180
Well,

1036
00:44:34,180 --> 00:44:35,820
I don't really know.

1037
00:44:37,980 --> 00:44:40,500
(Fengyang Bus Station)

1038
00:44:48,540 --> 00:44:49,650
11:45 PM.

1039
00:44:50,300 --> 00:44:51,140
Thanks, bro.

1040
00:44:51,380 --> 00:44:52,500
Don't mention it.

1041
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:00,420
Take this.

1042
00:45:00,420 --> 00:45:01,260
Thanks, Dali.

1043
00:45:01,900 --> 00:45:02,740
Dali,

1044
00:45:02,740 --> 00:45:04,640
once you leave,
you're really not coming back?

1045
00:45:05,900 --> 00:45:06,810
A man of his word

1046
00:45:06,810 --> 00:45:07,780
never goes back on it.

1047
00:45:07,780 --> 00:45:09,400
I don't want to go on about it with him.

1048
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:10,820
You're a real man.

1049
00:45:11,380 --> 00:45:12,220
Well, I'm off.

1050
00:45:12,580 --> 00:45:13,420
Safe travels.

1051
00:45:13,420 --> 00:45:14,260
Keep in touch.

1052
00:45:25,580 --> 00:45:26,420
Hey, mister.

1053
00:45:27,460 --> 00:45:28,530
Want to have some fun?

1054
00:45:29,660 --> 00:45:30,500
How much?

1055
00:45:31,360 --> 00:45:32,200
For the whole night,

1056
00:45:33,060 --> 00:45:34,080
one hundred and twenty.

1057
00:45:36,020 --> 00:45:38,160
My bus leaves in a bit at 11:30 PM.

1058
00:45:38,500 --> 00:45:39,340
Make it cheaper.

1059
00:45:39,740 --> 00:45:42,010
Mister, are we really haggling over this?

1060
00:45:45,620 --> 00:45:46,500
I'm fast,

1061
00:45:47,020 --> 00:45:48,020
really fast.

1062
00:45:48,980 --> 00:45:49,820
Make it cheaper.

1063
00:45:51,540 --> 00:45:52,740
Fine, I'll take the loss.

1064
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:54,780
I'll let you go

1065
00:45:55,580 --> 00:45:56,540
at 11:30 PM.

1066
00:45:57,100 --> 00:45:57,940
Eighty.

1067
00:45:58,100 --> 00:45:58,940
Deal.

1068
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:01,380
Where to?

1069
00:46:02,380 --> 00:46:03,220
I have a place.

1070
00:46:23,940 --> 00:46:24,780
Mister,

1071
00:46:25,660 --> 00:46:26,860
don't be in such a hurry.

1072
00:46:27,820 --> 00:46:29,110
Let me give you a massage first.

1073
00:46:36,860 --> 00:46:38,540
Mister, don't be in such a hurry.

1074
00:46:38,540 --> 00:46:40,580
Mister, go wash up first.

1075
00:46:40,580 --> 00:46:42,320
Go wash up first.

1076
00:46:42,580 --> 00:46:44,220
Wash what? No need for that.

1077
00:46:45,220 --> 00:46:46,460
You dare to sleep with my wife?

1078
00:46:47,300 --> 00:46:48,140
Kill him!

1079
00:46:54,940 --> 00:46:55,940
Hit him hard!

1080
00:46:55,940 --> 00:46:56,780
Beat him to death.

1081
00:46:57,100 --> 00:46:57,980
What took you so long?

1082
00:46:58,380 --> 00:47:00,200
I was afraid
you hadn't reeled him in yet.

1083
00:47:00,620 --> 00:47:01,820
Once they're in this room,

1084
00:47:01,820 --> 00:47:03,020
is there anyone I can't handle?

1085
00:47:07,920 --> 00:47:09,730
This one today is a big customer.

1086
00:47:09,730 --> 00:47:11,170
Yeah, that's quite a lot of cash.

1087
00:47:12,050 --> 00:47:12,890
Alright.

1088
00:47:13,080 --> 00:47:13,920
Stop hitting him.

1089
00:47:14,220 --> 00:47:15,120
Leave him some breath.

1090
00:47:15,780 --> 00:47:16,700
Let's go.

